        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-title" id="rules">Tournament Rules</h2>
      <div class="rules-container">
        <div class="rules-grid">
          <div class="rule-card highlight-rule">
            <h4>üìπ Mandatory POV Recording</h4>
            <p>Each team MUST have at least <strong>one player</strong> recording continuous POV (with team audio) for every match. Failure to provide POV when requested may result in disqualification.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Team Format</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Squad (4 Primary + 1 Sub)</li>
              <li>32-40 Total Squads</li>
              <li>4 Groups (A, B, C, D)</li>
              <li>College ID: Min 2 players/squad</li>
              <li>Top 4/group advance to Finals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Scoring System</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>1st Place: 10 pts | 2nd: 6 pts</li>
              <li>3rd: 5 pts | 4th: 4 pts</li>
              <li>5th: 3 pts | 6th: 2 pts</li>
              <li>7th: 1 pt | 8th-16th: 0 pts</li>
              <li>Kill Point: 1 per elim</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Game Settings</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Classic TPP Mode</li>
              <li>Mobile / Tab / iPad (No Emulators)</li>
              <li>Map Rotation: Era/Mir/Ron/San</li>
              <li>Registration: Via Google Form</li>
              <li>Online Quals & LAN Finals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="rule-card">
            <h4><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> Fair Play</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>No Cheats/GFX Tools</li>
              <li>No Account Sharing</li>
              <li>Must use Registered UID/IGN</li>
              <li>Stream Delay: Min 3-5 mins</li>
              <li>Admins' Decision is Final</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
